    *   `OFFLINE_FILE_NAME`: Defines the name of the file for offline capture. This file (`example.pcap`) **must exist** and contain valid pcap data for the offline part of the example to work. If it doesn't exist, `pcap_open_offline` will fail, and the offline section will be skipped.
